 1. the chef is in the middle##1
 2. the writer is not the person who's hobby is dancing##6
 3. the fisherman is not to the left of the mechanic##8
 4. the writer is between the mechanic and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
 8. the fisherman is not to the left of the entrepreneur##8
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
10. the entrepreneur is on the left of the fisherman##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
12. the designer is not to the right of the entrepreneur##8
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
14. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
15. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
16. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |      6      |      7      |
